message.text:
FEU Manila at the 35th MAP International CEO Conference 2025 

On September 9, 2025, FEU Manila proudly joined the 35th MAP International CEO Conference held at Shangri-La The Fort, Manila, with the theme “Leading Amidst Invisible Disruptions: Agility and Resilience in a Multipolar Era.”

Four delegates represented FEU Manila in this prestigious gathering: Dr. Maria Teresa Martinez, Dr. Jan Frederick Tongol, Maria Andrea Duqueza, President of OJFINEX, and Raffy Tagalog, President of EMS.

This event brought together visionary leaders, top executives, and changemakers from various industries to discuss global challenges and the future of leadership in a rapidly shifting world. FEU Manila’s participation highlights our commitment to fostering strong academic-industry linkages, empowering our student leaders, and staying engaged with thought leadership at the highest level.

#FEUManila #MAPCEOConference2025 #Leadership #Innovation #FutureRead

message.text:
FEU Manila at the 35th MAP International CEO Conference 2025 

On September 9, 2025, FEU Manila proudly joined the 35th MAP International CEO Conference held at Shangri-La The Fort, Manila, with the theme “Leading Amidst Invisible Disruptions: Agility and Resilience in a Multipolar Era.”

Four delegates represented FEU Manila in this prestigious gathering: Dr. Maria Teresa Martinez, Dr. Jan Frederick Tongol, Maria Andrea Duqueza, President of OJFINEX, and Raffy Tagalog, President of EMS.

This event brought together visionary leaders, top executives, and changemakers from various industries to discuss global challenges and the future of leadership in a rapidly shifting world. FEU Manila’s participation highlights our commitment to fostering strong academic-industry linkages, empowering our student leaders, and staying engaged with thought leadership at the highest level.

#FEUManila #MAPCEOConference2025 #Leadership #Innovation #FutureRead
